Class factory for Pack200.Packer and Pack200.Unpacker.

从以下版本开始：
Android 1.0

嵌套类摘要
static interface Pack200.Packer
          The interface defining the API for converting a JAR file to an output stream in the Pack200 format.
static interface Pack200.Unpacker
          The interface defining the API for converting a packed stream in the Pack200 format to a JAR file.
 
方法摘要
static Pack200.Packer newPacker()
          Returns a new instance of a packer engine.
static Pack200.Unpacker newUnpacker()
          Returns a new instance of a unpacker engine.

方法详细信息

newPacker

public static Pack200.Packer newPacker()
Returns a new instance of a packer engine.

The implementation of the packer engine is defined by the system property 'java.util.jar.Pack200.Packer'. If this system property is defined an instance of the specified class is returned, otherwise the system's default implementation is returned.

返回：
an instance of Packer
从以下版本开始：
Android 1.0

newUnpacker

public static Pack200.Unpacker newUnpacker()
Returns a new instance of a unpacker engine.

The implementation of the unpacker engine is defined by the system property 'java.util.jar.Pack200.Unpacker'. If this system property is defined an instance of the specified class is returned, otherwise the system's default implementation is returned.

返回：
a instance of Unpacker.
从以下版本开始：
Android 1.0
